version 2.0.5   2024-09-02
  1.Added point cloud masking function, which is used by the wlr-720 series lidar
  2.All lidars use the same point cloud coordinate system
  3.Optimize IMU algorithm, improve the accuracy of temperature compensation algorithm
  4.Add point cloud output logic, when IMU is enabled, point cloud output needs to wait for IMU calibration to be completed
  5.Compatibility with wlr-718x point cloud intensity value not enabled

version 2.0.6   2024-09-03
  1.Resolve the bug of assigning function parameters and IMU parameter structure to the universal version protocol, and store the checksum using "uingt16_t"
  2.Synchronization wlr-760 protocol analysis, update the time difference between the first and last points in the same circle to 74ms
  3.Added WLR-722 protocol parsing and IMU parsing
  4.The IMU coordinate system is consistent with the lidar (the wire direction is X-)

version 2.0.7   2024-09-06
  1.Update wlr-719c point cloud analysis
